[src:dayjs-datetime/global-objects-date] Due to the differing lengths of days (due to daylight saving changeover), months, and years, expressing elapsed time in units greater than hours, minutes, and seconds requires addressing a number of issues, and should be thoroughly researched before being attempted.
[src:dayjs-datetime/global-objects-date] In this case, it's important to return only an integer—so a simple division won't do.
